c5a2d490-cae7-418d-819c-ad31ed1e8d92.title: Turael
c5a2d490-cae7-418d-819c-ad31ed1e8d92.text: 'Ello, and what are you after then?

options.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?
Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.
遰 I'm here about a quest.

ac40e68a-4db3-4a5b-9b27-ff1bde1ca456.title: Turael
ac40e68a-4db3-4a5b-9b27-ff1bde1ca456.text:
You're still meant to be slaying <slayer_task_type>(s),
you have <slayer_task_remaining> to go.

7bbf1f79-d8d6-4f78-af55-9a91ee17a32b.title: Turael
7bbf1f79-d8d6-4f78-af55-9a91ee17a32b.text:
Although, it's not an assignment that I'd normally
give... I guess I could give you a new assignment,
if you'd like.

a5081a26-73eb-4faa-9f47-fc2af6320a1a.title: Turael
a5081a26-73eb-4faa-9f47-fc2af6320a1a.text:
If you do get a new one, you will reset your standard
task streak of <slayer_task_streak_normal>. Is that okay? It
won't affect your Wilderness task streak of <slayer_task_streak_wilderness>.

c60cf79a-4def-41df-9446-a3d8d645dd87.title: <player>
c60cf79a-4def-41df-9446-a3d8d645dd87.text: Have you any rewards for me, or anything to trade?

df3ae6c2-a7b4-45b6-bba6-5f759da5296c.title: Turael
df3ae6c2-a7b4-45b6-bba6-5f759da5296c.text:
I have quite a few rewards you can earn, and a wide
variety of Slayer equipment for sale.

13331d09-34f0-4007-92b2-382ea6191268.title: <player>
13331d09-34f0-4007-92b2-382ea6191268.text: Let's talk about the difficulty of my assignments.

9bd2f4ae-a1bb-452f-a863-d08668a36507.title: Turael
9bd2f4ae-a1bb-452f-a863-d08668a36507.text:
The Slayer Masters will take your combat level into
account when choosing tasks for you, so you shouldn't
get anything too hard.

9c7d96f2-27f3-4c21-8ec5-581bbe048ac1.title: Turael
9c7d96f2-27f3-4c21-8ec5-581bbe048ac1.text:
Ahh, you came to the right man; odd things, those trees.
What is it you are needing exactly?

e46934ee-ba09-456b-8104-87d658b9251f.title: <player>
e46934ee-ba09-456b-8104-87d658b9251f.text:
I'm here about a quest. Ava said she saw you hanging
around the moving trees near Draynor Manor.

4c022b9f-ed9a-4549-a48a-371309c13604.title: <player>
4c022b9f-ed9a-4549-a48a-371309c13604.text:
I think I need some of the wood from them, but my
axe just bounced off the trunk.

6e0985d5-9152-4253-bdae-38c863d9e13f.title: Turael
6e0985d5-9152-4253-bdae-38c863d9e13f.text:
Sounds like you need a blessed axe. No one really
makes them, though, these days.

1b52048d-d54f-4178-b5de-0c1152f20deb.title: Turael
1b52048d-d54f-4178-b5de-0c1152f20deb.text:
Blessed axes are too soft to cut normal wood since the
axe's edge must be replaced by holy silver. I can do
you a favour, though.

b33d2ee3-27c2-40ad-85ea-288d173e914a.title: Turael
b33d2ee3-27c2-40ad-85ea-288d173e914a.text:
If you can give me a mithril axe and a holy symbol of
Saradomin I can let you have my axe. I'll make myself
a new one when no one is pestering me for Slayer
tasks.

90b61432-c2c8-49a8-9bd5-6ee9ee857bb9.title: <player>
90b61432-c2c8-49a8-9bd5-6ee9ee857bb9.text:
Okay, so I'll see whether I can spare an axe and a
symbol. Thanks.

4796e5a5-8d25-4ca3-83f9-600c0faa2f7b.title: <player>
4796e5a5-8d25-4ca3-83f9-600c0faa2f7b.text: Hello, I'm here about those trees again.

2161745a-23bf-4d8b-8c2c-6f9715ac969d.title: Turael
2161745a-23bf-4d8b-8c2c-6f9715ac969d.text:
I can make an axe for you now, if you wish.
Remember, it will be no use for normal woodcutting
after I have added the silver edge.

ab46900a-4377-4314-9a47-c3d33ef719b0.title: Turael
ab46900a-4377-4314-9a47-c3d33ef719b0.text:
You'll need to hand over both a mithril axe and holy
symbol of Saradomin. You don't have a symbol in your
pack, so I'm not able to help.

beb041ad-dc60-4e07-be68-33c66572872a.title: Turael
beb041ad-dc60-4e07-be68-33c66572872a.text: Here's a new axe; may it serve you well.

24d5c4d9-f921-495a-8bb7-9ede01895fd9.title: Turael
24d5c4d9-f921-495a-8bb7-9ede01895fd9.text:
Goodbye, then. You may, of course, return if you
decide you want a new axe.

09f34d50-3cb0-4c77-9dfd-6aa7b4226b02.title: <player>
09f34d50-3cb0-4c77-9dfd-6aa7b4226b02.text: Hello, I'm here about the blessed axe again.

1b018179-bd5c-4d37-8c8f-a8980c4b8a9a.title: Turael
1b018179-bd5c-4d37-8c8f-a8980c4b8a9a.text:
You already have an axe in your bag but you want
another?

options.text: I can do without for now, thanks.

87b45e5c-d2cf-4072-86d7-414ed2d95501.title: Turael
87b45e5c-d2cf-4072-86d7-414ed2d95501.text: I suppose you want a new axe?

options.text: I can do without for now, thanks.

8dc991e0-b5df-4b9e-9da1-03c924b5bbfc.title: Turael
8dc991e0-b5df-4b9e-9da1-03c924b5bbfc.text:
Goodbye, then. You may, of course, return if you
decide you want a new axe.

d7b6068d-e58b-4b33-8708-2d6e8a6478a9.title: Turael
d7b6068d-e58b-4b33-8708-2d6e8a6478a9.text:
You'll need to hand over both a mithril axe and holy
symbol of Saradomin. You don't have a symbol in your
pack, so I'm not able to help.

d9fd1776-4e7a-4da1-af2d-eef5207e22ea.title: Turael
d9fd1776-4e7a-4da1-af2d-eef5207e22ea.text:
Here's the replacement; be more careful with this one,
eh?
